replies.body:
I've mained both for months at a time. Zed is easier to farm with, has a safer laning phase, is easier to juke teams with, and can pull off some nasty turn-around assassinations with his untargetability on his ultimate.

Talon, while I do agree he can delete carries by jumping to them, Has one way to get in and he has to literally **walk away from a team whose carry you just killed.** I've stopped many Talons late game by CC'ing them right when they E to my carries. It's so easy to tell because Talon does the **same damn thing every time.** Don't know where he is when he stealths? Gee, I wonder if there was a 100 gold solution...
